data.description: Well maintained 4-bedroom 3 full bath home on over 1 acre lot.  Nature lovers must see!  Inviting great room with exposed beams and cozy fireplace. Fresh paint, new carpet, newer roof, new water heater new HVAC 2022, new Renewable window by Anderson. Solid surface counter tops and tile backsplash. Sliding glass door opens to deck with fenced in back yard area for grilling. Very convenient to shopping, medical facilities and interstate.
